		<!-- CLUE ANSWER QUESTIONS -->

	<tag id="ID_CLUE_QUESTION_1"><![CDATA[What evidence shows that the suspect was at the crime scene?]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_CLUE_QUESTION_2"><![CDATA[Who has access to the drug found in our victim's body?]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_CLUE_QUESTION_3"><![CDATA[Who bit our victim before his death?]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_CLUE_QUESTION_4"><![CDATA[Where did the death of the victim likely occur?]]></tag>
